gobblin.eventhub.writer

Class BatchedEventhubDataWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.writer.BufferedAsyncDataWriter<String>
      • gobblin.eventhub.writer.BatchedEventhubDataWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AsyncDataWriter<String>, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class BatchedEventhubDataWriter
extends BufferedAsyncDataWriter<String>
    A batch writer for eventhub, composed by EventhubBatchAccumulator and EventhubDataWriter EventhubBatchAccumulator provides a buffer to store pending records EventhubDataWriter is the actual writer ships data to eventhub
